 salt","3 tbsp all-purpose flour","2 oz heavy whipping cream"]}],"id":"r254084","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-dxMr0tWLZWc\/XZQH9IHOA2I\/AAAAAAAAcN4\/5DCMVTS4O6c_I4RG-lPcoi5o_A3VN107wCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_ub4nooYUQrz3EMir.png","title":"Chicken Roulade with Prosciutto and Cheese","publishedAt":"2017-09-22T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"37 g","fat":"32 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"30 g","calories":"2402 kJ \/ 574 kcal"},"usefulItems":"rolling pin, serving platter, cling wrap","hintsAndTricks":["Serve with mashed potatoes and steamed green beans."],"basicInfo":["easy","40m","1h 5m","4 portions"]}